          "<snip>",
          "INFO: running command: `git submodule update --init --recursive` (cwd: /tmp/ltests-88arihe3/test_generate_examples_1/lightning-1/reckless/lightningd/plugins)",
          "INFO: running command: `git checkout HEAD` (cwd: /tmp/ltests-88arihe3/test_generate_examples_1/lightning-1/reckless/lightningd/plugins/summary)",
          "INFO: Your branch is up to date with 'origin/master'.",
          "INFO: using installer pythonuvshebang",
          "INFO: running command: `git rev-parse HEAD` (cwd: /tmp/ltests-88arihe3/test_generate_examples_1/lightning-1/reckless/lightningd/plugins/summary)",
          "INFO: 002761088174c151237e8a847c50603db20d5abf",
