          "INFO: Plugins matching 'summary':",
          "INFO:   summary (/media/addonssd/dev/plugins/summary)",
          "INFO: found summary in source: /media/addonssd/dev/plugins/summary",
          "INFO: Sending 1000msat to summary author...",
          "INFO: Successfully sent 1000msat to summary author!"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
